data.description: Welcome to your own private sanctuary in Woodbridge, where every corner is bursting with charm and flavor! As you explore this delightful home, you'll notice not only the sleek stainless steel kitchen appliances but also the promise of delicious adventures awaiting in the backyard.  Step outside and discover a true gardener's paradise! Imagine plucking ripe figs, crisp apples, and juicy peaches straight from the trees. Your mornings just got sweeter with the scent of magnolia blooms drifting through the air, and don't forget the irresistible allure of fresh raspberries and pears just waiting to be picked. Plus, indulge your green thumb fantasies with your very own grape vines, promising the potential for homemade wine or simply enjoying the fruits of your labor.  And nestled among this bounty is your master suite, offering the perfect blend of luxury and convenience with ensuite laundry facilities. It's not just a home; it's a lifestyle—a place where every day feels like a delicious adventure waiting to unfold. Come and experience the magic for yourself!
